Author: gentlerose
Text: I restricted during my finals and I regret it so much every day. I know I could’ve done so much better than I did had I just allowed myself to eat enough or in a surplus... I starved myself during one of the most important times of my life and have nothing to show for it, aside from embarrassment and shame. Please don’t do that to yourself. It really isn’t worth it :( Regardless, good luck with your studies.

Author: ks788
Text: Definitely eat because you’ll regret it if you don’t.
